(2, 'en', 3, 'About', 'about', '<p>We are a wonderful free online classified ads website for 2 cities: Los angeles and San Diego.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319342751, 1321411400, 1),
(3, 'en', 3, 'Terms of Use', 'terms-of-use', '<p>By accessing to our website you are agreeing to the following terms.</p>\n\n<p>Using Our website you will post in the appropriate category or area and will not do any of the following bad things:</p>\n\n<p>-  violate any laws or our Prohibited Content Policy;</p>\n\n<p>-  be false or misleading;</p>\n\n<p>-  infringe any third-party right;</p>\n\n<p>-  distribute or contain spam, chain letters, or pyramid schemes;</p>\n\n<p>-  distribute viruses or any other technologies that may harm Our website or the interests or property of Our website users;</p>\n\n<p>-  impose an unreasonable load on our infrastructure or interfere with the proper working of the Our website;</p>\n\n<p>-  copy, modify, or distribute any other person''s content;</p>\n\n<p>-  use any robot, spider, scraper or other automated means to access Our website and collect content for any purpose without our express written permission;</p>\n\n<p>-  harvest or otherwise collect information about others, including email addresses, without their consent;</p>\n\n<p>-  bypass measures used to prevent or restrict access to Our website.</p>', '<p>Abusing Our website. Please use the flagging system to tell us about any problems or offensive content so that together we can keep the site working properly. We may limit or terminate our service, remove hosted content and take technical and legal steps to keep users off Our website if we think that they are creating problems or acting inconsistently with the letter or spirit of our policies. However, whether we decide to take any of these steps, remove hosted content or keep a user off Our website or not, we do not accept any liability for monitoring Our website or for unauthorized or unlawful content on Our website or use of Our website by users.</p>\n\n<p>Fees and Services. Using Our website is generally free. We may charge fees for certain services. If the service you use charges a fee, you''ll be able to review and accept that charge. If your payment method fails or your account is past due, we may collect fees owed using other collection mechanisms (for accounts over 180 days past due, we may deduct the amount owed from your PayPal account balance).</p>\n\n<p>Content. Our website contains stuff from us, you, and other users. You agree not to copy, modify, or distribute Our website, our copyrights or trademarks. When you give us content, you are granting us a non-exclusive, worldwide, perpetual, irrevocable, royalty-free, sub-licensable right to exercise the copyright, publicity, and database rights to that content. (We need these rights to host and display your content.) If you believe that your rights have been violated, please notify our designated copyright agent at Our website Customer Support and we will investigate the matter. We reserve the right to remove content where we have grounds for suspecting the violation of these terms or of any party''s rights.</p>\n\n<p>Reporting Intellectual Property Infringements. Do not post content that infringes the rights of third parties. This includes, but is not limited to, content that infringes on intellectual property rights such as copyright and trademark (e.g. offering counterfeit items for sale). We reserve the right to remove content where we have grounds for suspecting the violation of these terms, our policies or of any party''s rights. The following steps are for reporting a listing to Our website that you believe to be infringing on your intellectual property rights. Only the intellectual property rights owner can report of potentially infringing items or listings through.</p>\n\n<p>Liability. You agree not to hold us responsible for things other users post or do. As most of the stuff on Our website comes from other users, we do not guarantee the accuracy of postings or user communications or the quality, safety, or legality of what''s offered. We also cannot guarantee continuous or secure access to our services. Accordingly, to the extent legally permitted we expressly disclaim all warranties, representations and conditions, express or implied, including those of quality, merchantability, merchantable quality, durability, fitness for a particular purpose and those arising by statute. We are not liable for any loss, whether of money (including profit), goodwill, or reputation, or any special, indirect, or consequential damages arising out of your use of Our website, even if you advise us or we could reasonably foresee the possibility of any such damage occurring. Some jurisdictions do not allow the disclaimer of warranties or exclusion of damages, so such disclaimers and exclusions may not apply to you.</p>\n\n<p>Personal Information. By using Our website, you agree to the collection, transfer, storage and use of your personal information.</p>', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319343489, 1335494572, 1),
(4, 'en', 4, 'Is it free to post ads?', 'is-it-free-to-post-ads', '<p>Yes, 100% free!</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319347919, 1319448998, 1),
(5, 'en', 4, 'Do I have to register to post ads?', 'do-i-have-to-register-to-post-ads', '<p>No. You can browse the site and post items without registration. <br /> However if you register you can manage your postings favourite ads and personal information even easier through the ''My account'' section of the site.</p>\n\n<p>Registration is free and the process is very simple: <br /> Click on "Register" button and you will be asked to provide your basic contact information. You will then receive a confirmation message with your password information to your email address.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319347960, 1319449047, 1),
(6, 'en', 4, 'How do I edit a posting?', 'how-do-i-edit-a-posting', '<p>If you are a registered user, sign in, click My Account then click My ads. Click the Edit icon next to the Ad you would like to change.</p>\n\n<p>Remember you don''t have to register to post ads. If you did not go through the optional registration process, then you can change your ad by using the Edit link found in the posting confirmation email we sent you when you posted your Ad.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319347986, 1319449092, 1),
(7, 'en', 4, 'How do I remove my posting?', 'how-do-i-remove-my-posting', '<p>If you have an account, you can end your ad in my ads section by clicking the â€œDeleteâ€ icon.Â </p>\n\n<p>If you don''t have an account yet, you can click the link enclosed in the confirmation email you receive upon posting an item on the site. Then you will be able to delete the ad.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319348021, 1319449152, 1),
(9, 'en', 4, 'What is not allowed?', 'what-is-not-allowed', '<p>The list below details what can''t be posted:</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Adult or Erotic Products and Services</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Alcoholic Beverages</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Baby Walkers</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Blood, Bodily Fluids and Body Parts</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Burglary Tools</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Counterfeit currency, stamps or coins</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Counterfeit Products</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Electronic Surveillance Equipment designed or used primarily to illegally intercept/record the private actions or interactions of others without their knowledge or permission</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Embargoed Goods</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Escort or accompanying services</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Government and Transit Uniforms, IDs and Licenses</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Illegal Drugs &amp; Drug Paraphernalia</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Illegal Services</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Hazardous Materials</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Fireworks, Destructive Devices and Explosives</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Identity Documents, Personal Financial Records &amp; Personal Information (in any form, including mailing lists)</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Items which encourage or facilitate illegal activity (such as mod chips or modding services)</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Lottery Tickets, Sweepstakes Entries and Slot Machines</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Massage services</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  New merchandise or services from network marketing companies, independent franchisees or distributors, or similar representatives*</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Obscene Material and Child Pornography</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Offensive Material</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Pesticides</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Pictures or images that contain nudity</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Police Badges and Uniforms</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Prescription Drugs and Devices</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Prostitution or ads that offer sex, sexual favours or sexual actions in exchange for money</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Recalled items</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Satellite products that violate the Radiocommunication Act</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Sexual services, including webcamming</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Solicitation of other users except by placing an Ad</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Stocks and Other Securities</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Stolen Property</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Tobacco Products</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Used Cosmetics</p>\n\n<p>Â Â Â  Weapons and related items (such as firearms, firearm parts and magazines, ammunition, BB and pellet guns, tear gas, stun guns, knives, archery equipment, and martial arts weapons)</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319449229, 1319449229, 1),
(10, 'en', 4, 'How long do ads last on the site?', 'how-long-do-ads-last-on-the-site', '<p>Ads are automatically removed from the site 60 days after being posted.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319449289, 1319449289, 1),
(11, 'en', 4, 'What should I do if I see an ad that I think is not allowed?', 'what-should-i-do-if-i-see-an-ad-that-i-think-is-not-allowed', '<p>If you see an ad which you think is illegal, prohibited or otherwise a bad fit for the site, please report it by clicking one of the "Repor this ad" links.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319449371, 1319449371, 1),
(12, 'en', 4, 'What are Top ads?', 'what-are-top-ads', '<p>Top ads are ads that have been upgraded to also appear in the "Top ads" section at the top of a category listing page for several days. More people read and reply to these Ads because of their prominent position on the first page of a category over a long time period. Simply put, buying a Top ad is the best way to help sell your item.</p>\n\n<p>Note that if more than 5 Top ads are purchased in a category, only a random five will be shown. The ads which are randomly picked will change each time you look at the page.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319449434, 1319449434, 1),
(13, 'en', 4, 'What is the Homepage Gallery?', 'what-is-the-homepage-gallery', '<p>The Homepage Gallery is a special section at the top of the homepage where ads can be displayed. These ads are the most viewed because of their prominent position on the homepage. The Homepage Gallery option can be bought when you post an ad.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1319449491, 1319449491, 1),
(14, 'fr', 3, 'A propos', 'a-propos', '<div class="almost_half_cell">\n<div dir="ltr"><span lang="fr" xml:lang="fr"><span>Nous sommes un site de petites annonces gratuites en ligne.<br /><br /></span></span></div>\n</div>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335956553, 1),
(15, 'fr', 3, 'Conditions d''utilisation', 'conditions-dutilisation', '<p>En utilisant notre site vous acceptez les conditions d’utilisation suivantes:<br />Vous vous engagez à poster vos annonces dans les catégories appropriées et à ne pas adopter l’un des comportements listés ci-dessous:<br /><br />-  violer la loi de votre pays;<br />-  poster des announces trompeuses;<br />-  porter atteinte aux droits d’un tiers;<br />-  procéder à l’envoi de spams;<br />-  propager des virus;<br />-  copier, modifier, ou distribuer le contenu publié par un tiers;<br />-  utiliser un robot.<br /><br /></p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335956571, 1),
(16, 'fr', 4, 'Est-il gratuit de poster des annonces ?', 'est-il-gratuit-de-poster-des-annonces', '<p>Oui, 100% gratuit !</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335956607, 1),
(17, 'fr', 4, 'Dois-je être membre pour pouvoir poster une annonce ?', 'dois-je-tre-membre-pour-pouvoir-poster-une-annonce', '<p>Non. Vous pouvez visiter le site et poster des annonces sans être membre.<br /><br />Cependant si vous devenez membre vous pourrez gérer vos annonces favorites et gérer vos informations personnelles plus facilement depuis votre zone "Membre''.<br /><br />Vous inscrire sur le site est très simple:<br />cliq</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335946608, 1),
(18, 'fr', 4, 'Comment modifier une annonce ?', 'comment-modifier-une-annonce', '<p>Si vous êtes membre, veuillez vous connecter, cliquer sur "Mon compte'' puis sur "Mes annonces". Cliquez ensuite l''icone pour modifier l''annonce de votre choix.</p>\n<p>Vous n''avez pas besoin de vous inscrire pour poster des annonces. Si vous n''êtes pas membre vous pouvez modifier vos annonces grâce au lien contenu dans le mail de confirmation de chacune de vos annonces.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335956672, 1),
(19, 'fr', 4, 'Comment supprimer une de mes annonces ?', 'comment-supprimer-une-de-mes-annonces', '<p>If you have an account, you can end your ad in my ads section by clicking the â€œDeleteâ€ icon.Â </p>\n<p>Si vous êtes membre, vous pouvez supprimer une de vos annonces depuis la zone Membre.<br /><br />Si vous n''êtes pas membre, vous pouvez le faire en cliquant sur le lien de modification inclu dans l''email de confirmation pour chacune de vos annonces.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335956638, 1),
(20, 'fr', 4, 'Quelles sont les annonces interdites ?', 'quelles-sont-les-annonces-interdites', '<p>Ne peuvent pas faire l''objet d''annonces:<br /><br />- Animaux, parties animales, et espèces végétales<br />- Armes à feu, explosifs, munitions, répliques et objets militaires<br />- Biens culturels et archives publiques<br />- Biens soumis à embargo<br />- Billets de loterie <br />- Cartes de crédit<br />- Contrats et billets   <br />- Documents officiels délivrés par l''Etat <br />- Décodeurs et autres matériels de décryptage<br />- Drogues, substances réglementées et objets associés<br />- Equipement de surveillance<br />- Fausses monnaies et faux timbres<br />- Feux d''artifice <br />- Incitation à des activités illégales<br />- Instruments financiers<br />- Listes de publipostage et données à caractère personnel<br />- Machines à affranchir<br />- Marchandises interdites ou réglementées<br />- Matériels destinés à l''ouverture des serrures<br />- Médicaments et parapharmacie<br />- Mini-motos, Pocket-Bikes, mini-quads et Quads non homologués<br />- Objets à caractère pédophile<br />- Objets volés ou recelés<br />- Organes et produits du corps humain<br />- Produits cosmétiques d''occasion<br />- Réservé aux adultes (contenus obscènes et/ou violents)<br />- Substances dangereuses et illicites<br />- Services interdits<br />- Tabac <br />- Violence, discrimination et haine raciale</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335957328, 1),
(21, 'fr', 4, 'Combien de temps les annonces restent-elles en ligne ?', 'combien-de-temps-les-annonces-restent-elles-en-ligne', '<p>Les annonces sont retirées après un délai de 60 jours.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335957423, 1),
(22, 'fr', 4, 'Que dois-je faire si je vois une annonce au contenu interdit ?', 'que-dois-je-faire-si-je-vois-une-annonce-au-contenu-interdit', '<p>Veuillez nous signaler l''existence de cette annonce en utilisant le lien "Signaler" une annonce au bas de la page de l''annonce.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335957387, 1),
(23, 'fr', 4, 'Que sont les Top annonces ?', 'que-sont-les-top-annonces', '<p>Les Top annonces sont des annonces qui apparaissent en plus de leur rang normal, dans une section spéciale, nommée "Top annonces" en haut des résultats, pour une durée prédéterminée. Davantage de gens voient ces annonces en raison de leur position en tête des résultats. <br /><br />S''il y a plus de 5 annonces dans la section Top annonces d''une même catégorie, 5 annonces seulement seront affichées à la fois mais toutes les annonces seront affichées un même nombre de fois sur 24 heures.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335957358, 1),
(24, 'fr', 4, 'Qu''est ce que la Galerie de page d''acceuil ?', 'que-est-ce-que-la-Galerie-de-page-daccueil', '<p>La Galerie de page d''accueil est une section spéciale en haut de la page d''accueil où des annonces sont affichées. Ces annonces sont beaucoup plus consultées que les annonces normales en raison de leur position sur la page d''accueil. Vous pouvez placer votre annonces dans cette section en cochant l''option correspondante au bas de la page de création d''une annonce.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335493434, 1335957457, 1),
(46, 'es', 4, '¿Que es la Galería de inicio?', 'que-es-la-galeria-de-inicio', '<p>Puedes destacar tu anuncio al publicarlo. Luego de presionar el botón "Publicar", verás una página que te permite destacar tu anuncio en la Galería de inicio. Haz click la cantidad de días/semanas que lo quieres destacar. Luego haz click en el botón "Promociona tu Anuncio". Aparecerá una página solicitando los datos de tu tarjeta de crédito para realizar el pago.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957546, 1),
(40, 'es', 4, '¿Cómo edito un anuncio?', 'como-edito-un-anuncio', '<p>Si tienes una cuenta, puedes editar tus publicaciones en la lista "Mis Anuncios", en la sección Mi cuenta del sitio. Por favor, ve al anuncio y haz click en el botón "Editar". Una vez que hayas modificado el anuncio y confirmado los cambios, los mismos serán visibles inmediatamente en tu anuncio. Puedes repetir este proceso siempre que lo desees. Si todavía no tienes una cuenta, también puedes acceder a las mismas funcionalidades utilizando los links del email que recibes cada vez que publicas un anuncio en el sitio.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957577, 1),
(41, 'es', 4, '¿Cómo elimino mi anuncio?', 'como-elimino-mi-anuncio', '<p>Si tienes una cuenta y vendiste tu producto o simplemente deseas dejar de publicarlo, puedes hacerlo a través de la opción ''Mis anuncios'' en la sección Mi cuenta del sitio. Haz click en la cajita a la izquierda del anuncio o anuncios que deseas dejar de publicar y luego haz click en el botón ‘Eliminar los anuncios seleccionados’. Si todavía no tienes una cuenta, puedes acceder a la misma funcionalidad usando el link dentro del email de confirmación recibido al publicar el anuncio en el sitio.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957610, 1),
(42, 'es', 4, '¿Que anuncios están prohibidos?', 'que-anuncios-estan-prohibidos', '<p>El usuario acepta no anunciar, enviar por email, ni poner a disposición en el Sitio contenido que:</p>\n<p>- sea contrario a la ley, la moral y las buenas costumbres;</p>\n<p>- viole una patente, marca, nombre comercial, denominación social, designación comercial, logo, nombre de dominio, diseño industrial, modelo de utilidad, secreto comercial, derecho de autor u otro derecho de propiedad intelectual o industrial de un Tercero, o Contenido respecto del cual el Usuario no tiene derecho a poner a disposición del público en virtud de una norma legal o una obligación contractual.</p>\n<p>- sea dañino, ilícito, amenazador, abusivo, acosador, difamatorio, pornográfico;</p>\n<p>- afecte la privacidad de terceros;</p>\n<p>- dañe a menores en cualquier forma;</p>\n<p>- sea discriminatorio respecto a un individuo o un grupo de individuos por su religión, género, orientación sexual, raza, etnia, edad o capacidad, convicciones políticas, morales, filosóficas; vinculación a asociaciones gremiales, etc.;</p>\n<p>- incluya información personal de terceros sin el consentimiento expreso de la persona mencionada.</p>\n<p>- sea falso, engañoso, constituya una falsa representación de la información o importe una forma de atracción de clientes modificando luego las condiciones ofrecidas;</p>\n<p>- constituya o contenga “marketing viral”, “código de referencias a enlace”, “spam”, “esquemas de pirámides” o publicidad comercial no solicitada.</p>\n<p>- publicite servicios ilícitos;</p>\n<p>- comercialice artículos cuya venta se encuentre prohibida o restringida por la ley aplicable;</p>\n<p>- contenga virus de software u otros códigos, archivos o programas de computación diseñados para interrumpir, destruir o limitar la funcionalidad de un software o de un hardware de computación o de un equipo de telecomunicaciones;</p>\n<p>- interrumpa el flujo normal del diálogo con una cantidad excesiva de mensajes al Servicio (ataque masivo), que de alguna forma afecte en forma nociva la capacidad de los Usuarios para utilizar el Servicio; y/o</p>\n<p>- utilice direcciones de email confusas, o encabezados falsos o que de otra forma manipule los identificadores a fin de ocultar el origen del Contenido transmitido a través del Servicio.</p>\n<p>Tal listado es meramente enunciativo.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957645, 1),
(43, 'es', 4, '¿Durante cuánto tiempo aparecerá mi anuncio en el sitio?', 'durante-cuanto-tiempo-aparecera-mi-anuncio-en-el-sitio', '<p>Actualmente los anuncios no caducan. Es tu responsabilidad eliminar tu anuncio cuando ya no necesitas promocionarlo más.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957699, 1),
(44, 'es', 4, '¿Qué puedo hacer si sospecho de un vendedor fraudulento?', 'que-puedo-hacer-si-sospecho-de-un-vendedor-fraudulento', '<p>Si sospechas que un anuncio del sitio es falso o fraudulento, por favor contáctanos.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957732, 1),
(45, 'es', 4, '¿Que es un anuncio destacado?', 'que-es-un-anuncio-destacado', '<p>Puedes destacar tu anuncio al publicarlo. Luego de presionar el botón "Publicar", verás una página que te permite destacar tu anuncio por encima de todos los otors anuncios. Haz click la cantidad de días/semanas que lo quieres destacar. Luego haz click en el botón "Promociona tu Anuncio". Aparecerá una página solicitando los datos de tu tarjeta de crédito para realizar el pago.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335949740, 1),
(38, 'es', 4, '¿Es gratis este sitio?', 'es-gratis-este-sitio', '<p>¡Si, 100% gratis!</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957754, 1),
(39, 'es', 4, '¿Debo registrarme para usar este sitio?', 'debo-registrarme-para-usar-este-sitio', '<p>No. Puedes navegar el sitio y publicar anuncios sin registrarte. Registrarse es gratuito y muy simple:<br /><br />- Haz click en "Registrarte" y completa la información básica de contacto.<br />- ¡Ya estás registrado!<br />- Te enviará un email con un link e instrucciones para confirmar tu registro.<br /><br />Una vez que tengas una cuenta, puedes administrar tus anuncios e información personal incluso más fácilmente desde la sección "Mi cuenta" del sitio.</p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957778, 1),
(36, 'es', 3, 'Acerca del sitio', 'acerca-del-sitio', '<p>Este sitio es la próxima generación de anuncios gratis online.<br /><br /><br /></p>', '', NULL, NULL, 1, 1335925249, 1335957794, 1),
